n by Penelope Green that gives the artist credit for mounting one of the fi=
rst conceptual art shows while teaching at SVA in the 1960s. As Green expla=
ined, Bochner believed conceptual work had to take some material form. Even=
tually, for
Bochner, that material form would be language.

=C2=A0

Anyway, I=E2=80=99m glad the Times got it together. The news organization c=
