n-bottom:0px;">The Riggios bought their painting 25 years ago. In 2015, the=
 1929 work sold at
auction for just above $50 million to the bond fund manager and museum patr=
on <strong>Jeffrey Gundlach</strong>. Six years later, a rectangular work f=
rom 1927 with a red section sold for $26 million. Then, in November of 2022=
