 sparsely trafficked, and went on to assert that it was =E2=80=9Ca go-to so=
urce for art
reviews among people who care(d) about those sorts of things. And the <em>N=
YT</em> does plenty of obits for less =E2=80=98prominent individuals.=E2=80=
=99=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=
=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Fair enough. I meant no disrespect to Robi=
